        </CharacterStyleRange>
      </ParagraphStyleRange>
    </Footnote>
  </CharacterStyleRange>
  <CharacterStyleRange AppliedCharacterStyle="$ID/NormalCharacterStyle">
    <Content> In editorials, writers waxed eloquent about its transformational possibilities. Madhu Valluri, a regular contributor to the </Content>
  </CharacterStyleRange>
  <CharacterStyleRange AppliedCharacterStyle="CharacterStyle/Italic">
    <Content>Times of India</Content>
  </CharacterStyleRange>
  <CharacterStyleRange AppliedCharacterStyle="$ID/NormalCharacterStyle">
    <Content>, wrote, for example, about how a computer system developed in the US to track and communicate environmental disasters could provide an ‘insight into what’s actually going on around us […] at a touch of a key’.</Content>
  </CharacterStyleRange>
  <CharacterStyleRange AppliedCharacterStyle="$ID/NormalCharacterStyle" Position="Superscript">
    <Footnote>
      <ParagraphStyleRange>
        <CharacterStyleRange>
          <Content><?ACE 4?></Content>
        </CharacterStyleRange>
      </ParagraphStyleRange>
      <ParagraphStyleRange AppliedParagraphStyle="ParagraphStyle/Footnote &gt; Paragraph">
        <CharacterStyleRange AppliedCharacterStyle="$ID/NormalCharacterStyle">
          <Content>	</Content>
        </CharacterStyleRange>
        <CharacterStyleRange AppliedCharacterStyle="$ID/NormalCharacterStyle">
          <Content>Madhu Valluri, ‘How Info-tech can Help Environment’, </Content>
        </CharacterStyleRange>
        <CharacterStyleRange AppliedCharacterStyle="CharacterStyle/Italic">
          <Content>The Times of India</Content>
        </CharacterStyleRange>
        <CharacterStyleRange AppliedCharacterStyle="$ID/NormalCharacterStyle">
